import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Button } from '@material-ui/core'

function Navbar() {
    return (
        <AppBar 
            position="static"
            color="transparent"
            elevation={0}
            className="navbar"
        >
            <Toolbar>
                <Typography variant="h6" className="navbar__title">
                    News
                </Typography>
                <Button color="inherit">Login</Button>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}

export default Navbar
